WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.590
WCAG stands for

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.580
Web Content Accessibility Guidelines,

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:09.550
which are published by 
the World Wide Web Consortium 
Web Accessibility Initiative

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.550
They provide guidelines and best practices 
for making web content accessible to everyone

00:00:15.590 --> 00:00:21.550
including people with 
visual, auditory, physical, cognitive and neurological impairments.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:24.500
WCAG 2.1 covers a wide range of topics

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:26.550
including text and images,

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:30.000
audio and video and adaptive technologies among others.
